07/19/07 20:25:05 brian [384]
	* trunk/wec_sermons/doc/manual.sxw (modified)
	* trunk/wec_sermons/pi1/class.tx_wecsermons_pi1.php (modified)
	- Improvement: Added a check for proper loading of searchbox subpart
	- New Feature: Added processing to the startDate and endDate
	properties within listView and latestView, which accepts the function
	'date()' to calculate todays date. This allows one to specify a
	moving window of records to be shown, such as 'date()-365'.
	- Bugfix: startDate and endDate now filter series records, if a non-
	grouped list of series records is chosen.
	- Updated documentation
	- Removed trailing spaces

07/19/07 02:26:28 brian [383]
	* trunk/wec_sermons/pi1/class.tx_wecsermons_pi1.php (modified)
	- Rolled back bugfix for series season and series topic logic checks,
	as this would cause mysql errors.

07/18/07 23:48:03 brian [382]
	* trunk/wec_sermons/doc/manual.sxw (modified)
	* trunk/wec_sermons/pi1/class.tx_wecsermons_pi1.php (modified)
	- Udated documentation with proper occurrence_date marker name
	- Bugfix: getSeriesResources and getSermonResources functions were
	filtering out single view records by the pid. The starting points
	should be obeyed for views other than single views.
	- Bugfix: Corrected series_season and series_topics subpart marker
	processing, as they were not saving current and previous row before
	changing context to related tables.

