07/09/07 15:09:35 brian [363]
	* trunk/wec_sermons/doc/manual.sxw (modified)
	* trunk/wec_sermons/pi1/class.tx_wecsermons_pi1.php (modified)
	* trunk/wec_sermons/static/constants.txt (modified)
	* trunk/wec_sermons/static/setup.txt (modified)
	- New Feature: Added the Smart Display option, allowing a user to
	turn off the auto-detection of SINGLE view requests. This is needed
	when you have two plugins enabled on a page, one set to always show a
	list or latest view, and the other showing a single view.

07/03/07 22:14:28 brian [362]
	* trunk/wec_sermons/pi1/class.tx_wecsermons_pi1.php (modified)
	- BUGFIX: Added a check for ###CONTENT### subpart marker for single,
	latest, and list views. If this is not available then it could throw
	Apache into a loop.

07/03/07 14:28:29 brian [361]
	* trunk/wec_sermons/pi1/class.tx_wecsermons_pi1.php (modified)
	- BUGFIX: list and latest views were using piVars['recordType'] to
	specify the current table, when this should be done from plugin or
	typoscript. Configured to set and use $this-&gt;internal['currentTable']

	- BUGFIX: Processing the ITEM part of a template when it was not
	present in grouped views caused the plugin to fail. Created branch
	that if ITEM subpart is not present, we do not try to process.

07/02/07 20:35:05 brian [356]
	* trunk/wec_sermons/ext_tables.php (modified)
	- BUGFIX: Resources were not ordering themselves by crdate
	descending, rather by crdate ascending and title descending. Moved
	the DESC keyword to the proper place.

