06/16/07 23:36:43 brian [343]
	* trunk/wec_sermons/pi1/class.tx_wecsermons_pi1.php (modified)
	- BUGFIX: Corrected an order of operations problem with grouped
	views. We were switching context to sermons before series were done.

	- BUGFIX: Corrected grouped output query. Searching for series uids
	within the sermons record was not returning the proper results. Now
	query uses find_in_set function to find series uids within the
	series.uid field.

